OL,3,CGuernsey Police warning over social
OL,4,Cmedia 'speculation'
OL,6,FGuernsey Police have warned against
OL,7,Fsharing unverified information on
OL,8,Fsocial media following two incidents
OL,9,Fagainst women in the island.
OL,11,FIn a statement on social media, police
OL,12,Fsaid that they attended two incidents
OL,13,Fon Monday 22 June, where women felt
OL,14,Funcomfortable due to the behaviour of
OL,15,Ftwo different men.
OL,17,F"One of these incidents related to
OL,18,Fphotographs taken at a beach and the
OL,19,Fother, a man approaching/speaking to
OL,20,Fwomen in St Peter Port," their
OL,21,Fstatement reads.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
