PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782416882
OL,3,CGuernsey Police warning over social
OL,4,Cmedia 'speculation'
OL,6,FPolice say that officers have carried
OL,7,Fout enquiries into both matters, but
OL,8,Fwere concerned after an influx of
OL,9,Fsocial media speculation on Tuesday 23
OL,10,FJune.
OL,12,FPolice are now calling on people to
OL,13,Freport "suspicious or concerning
OL,14,Factivity" directly to them, rather
OL,15,Fthan posting unverified information on
OL,16,Fsocial media.
OL,18,F"We are aware of social media posts
OL,19,Fcirculating in relation to both
OL,20,Fincidents," Guernsey police stated.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
