FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782416882
OL,3,CGuernsey Police warning over social
OL,4,Cmedia 'speculation'
OL,6,F"We would like to remind the community
OL,7,Fthat speculation and the sharing of
OL,8,Funverified claims can cause real and
OL,9,Flasting damage.
OL,11,F"Posts of this nature can escalate
OL,12,Fquickly, placing undue pressure on
OL,13,Findividuals and diverting police
OL,14,Fresources away from genuine policing
OL,15,Fneeds. They may also amount to
OL,16,Fharassment."
OL,18,FDue to recent hot weather, the police
OL,19,Fwill have additional patrols in places
OL,20,Fon beaches and beauty spots in the
OL,21,Fcoming days.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
